{
  "message": "Add dark mode support\n\n- Add dark: prefixed Tailwind classes across all components\n- Use neutral color palette instead of gray\n- Dark background (#1a1917) with warm tones to match light mode vibes\n- WaveSurfer waveform colors adapt to color scheme\n- Apple Podcasts button gets border in dark mode\n- Automatically follows browser's prefers-color-scheme\n\n\ud83d\udd2e View transcript: https://agentlogs.ai/s/yalx5y7jlor90xvzs96g7yz5",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "360ee8ab32086af4ebbad284c745426719355dbf",
